      "content": "800mg? wow okay. i'm a bit nervous about taking that much though. is it safe to take that along with some extra strong acetaminophen (paracetamol) to make sure the pain actually goes away so i can sleep? i really dont want to have to go to the er tonight if i can help it, it's so expensive",
